356
00:20:08,544 --> 00:20:09,970
<i>en la esquina de Murillo y Gurruchaga.</i>

357
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,940
<i>Te espero ahí a las 11:30.</i>

358
00:20:12,096 --> 00:20:13,200
<i>Igual si llegás tarde, te espero.</i>

359
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,590
[Claudia] <i>¿Vos cómo estás, bien?</i>

360
00:20:14,784 --> 00:20:15,808
[Galván] <i>Bastante bien.</i>

361
00:20:15,936 --> 00:20:17,510
<i>Ah, anotá mi celular,
