453
00:26:06,810 --> 00:26:09,000
Estamos, Santos.

454
00:26:09,232 --> 00:26:13,440
{\an8}[♫ LTJ Bukem -  James Bond Theme (remix) ♫]

455
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:19,072
{\an8}[♫ Frank Sinatra - The World We Knew ♫]

456
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:25,620
Bien, llamada en cinco, por favor.

457
00:26:25,744 --> 00:26:26,650
Cuatro.

458
00:26:26,752 --> 00:26:27,750
Tres.

