00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,264
Bien.

631
00:33:39,456 --> 00:33:41,550
{\an8}[♫ <i>In a little while from now</i> ♫]

632
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,960
{\an8}[♫ <i>If I'm not feeling any less sour</i> ♫]

